Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:42.97,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,How could this have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:46.16,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:48.96,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we totally fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:07.48,JoJo-MainTitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}JoJo's {\c&H2E0FB2&}Bizarre Adventure
