Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:34.95,Jojo-India,map,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(4426,1)}Saudi Arabia                                         India
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:34.95,Jojo-Pakistan,map,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(4426,1)}Pakistan\N\N{\fs14}Abu Dhabi                     Karachi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:34.95,Jojo-ArabianSea,map,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(4426,1)}Arabian Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:34.95,Jojo-Iran,map,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(4426,1)}Cairo                Iraq                  Iran
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.72,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro and company stopped\N The Lovers' cowardly attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:29.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,To avoid the politically unstable \Nroute from Iran to Iraq,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:32.03,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,they crossed the Arabian Sea at Karachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.48,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and entered the United Arab Emirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:38.97,JoJo-EpTitle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(483,1)}Episode 18: The Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.97,JoJo-top,person,0000,0000,0000,,Now, once you sign this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be under contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:44.30,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:53.05,JoJo-Location,blah,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:51.40,JoJo-top,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Man... If a cute girl like you asked me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.86,JoJo-top,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I might even buy them a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.36,JoJo-main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:58.74,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,How about we get dinner sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:04.78,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff, I'm terribly sorry to \Ninterrupt when you're so busy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.27,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.45,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.73,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Don't mess with the hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.85,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really hard to get this hairdo right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:16.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about your hairdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.31,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We need you to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:19.33,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Righto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.22,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.95,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But, man, Mr. Joestar,\N why are we riding in such a fancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.00,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,expensive car in this sandy place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.55,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Why not get an off-road vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.20,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.78,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But, man, I can't believe this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:50.79,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Every house we see is like a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.03,JoJo-main,jopseh,0000,0000,0000,,All the houses around here would
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.24,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,cost 3 or 4 billion yen in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:01.34,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, this is the norm for the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Just twenty years ago, this was all desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.98,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to massive profits from the oil crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.85,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,this place grew into a dream-like city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.78,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is harsh,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:16.19,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but with air conditioning, it's \Nperfectly comfortable inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,No complaints here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:20.82,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.76,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kakyoin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.12,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.25,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The view here is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.13,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone were after us, \NI'm sure we'd spot them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:33.46,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel like someone's watching us,\N so I can't help looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.74,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with that in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:41.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about our route from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:45.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,About 100 kilometers northwest\N is a village called Yarpline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:49.75,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the desert and mountains, \Nthe road is heavily curved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.44,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It takes two days to reach by car,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:56.14,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so the villagers use a Cessna to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:59.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should go to the village first,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:02.74,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,buy a Cessna, and cross the \Nvast Saudi Arabian desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.98,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now, I've been worried \Nthat attacks by Stand users
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.66,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,would cause any airplane we rode in to crash,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.85,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,putting innocent lives at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But if we have a Cessna, I can pilot it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.75,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll shorten our travel time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.65,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want to board a Cessna with a man
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.13,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who's been through three plane crashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.81,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.71,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should first cross this desert
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.97,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to get to the village of Yarpline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.95,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,On camels, it would take one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.58,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Camels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.12,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,A Cessna's one thing, but wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.30,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never ridden a camel before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:48.07,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know them very well.\N I'll teach you how to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:51.24,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Just sit back and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.25,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,You want camels?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.59,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but they're pretty expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.25,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,and not easy to care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.95,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a serious, life-or-death situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,so we need them, whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,As for payment, how about a trade for that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.26,JoJo-main,guy/jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.25,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.17,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.77,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you just bought that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:21.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Why else do you think I bought \Nsuch a fancy, expensive car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:24.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,An off-road vehicle is better in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:29.11,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't be able to\N write a check in a place like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.63,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and they don't trust cash here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:35.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,In a place like this, trading is far more effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:38.83,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to buy safety for cheap \Nin a time of emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll end up even worse off in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:46.32,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it just means we've suffered a lot already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:47.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.28,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.18,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This seals the deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:54.18,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know. To make things more even,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.77,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like the water in those tanks there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:00.84,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,In a desert, that's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:04.48,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Water is cheap compared to that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.28,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are an odd one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.64,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone. Let's get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:13.80,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Crossing a desert is a tough task.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.73,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep our wits about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.34,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I-It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:25.11,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.35,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you get on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's, like, three meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.22,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, with camels...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:34.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You make them sit first, and then get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:43.85,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You make them sit first, and then get on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.40,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You make them sit, then get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:52.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just one moment.\N It's gonna sit down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sit! Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you stubborn animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.50,JoJo-overlap,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you {\i1}have{\i0} ridden one of these before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:07.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen that really long movie, \N{\i1}Lawrence of Arabia{\i0}, three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.55,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know very well how to ride a camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:12.31,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Though, two of those times, \NI slept through half of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.07,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,M-Movie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:18.60,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What? You've never actually ridden one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:29.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's great sunscreen! Didn't you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.97,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:38.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,When dealing with animals, it's \Nimportant to understand how they feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly how they feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:44.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Here, doesn't this apple look delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.35,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:49.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Look! See?! It sat down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:57.46,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take time to understand the camel,\N it'll sit down for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.73,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:07.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's so high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.65,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,They can close their nostrils to keep sand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.73,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't make any stupid jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:18.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,like "Once you get over the hump,\N it's easy," or they'll kick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:23.54,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Now I'll tell you what to \Nbe careful with when riding camels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:25.14,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.29,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Camels don't walk like horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:31.29,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The front and back leg on the same side
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.84,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,move forward together, so they sway a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:38.76,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,So just ride with that rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.37,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.60,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! T-Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,L-Listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.50,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Not that way, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:58.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Looks like everyone \Ngot on as smoothly as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.62,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get through that desert, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Onward toward the northwest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.92,JoJo-main,jsoeph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.56,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:27.18,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't shake the feeling \Nthat someone's watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:35.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin, I think you're worrying a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.45,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The palm leaves are covering our tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.57,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,And we can see a great distance around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.33,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,If someone were here, we'd know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:49.39,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I can't help but feel a presence, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:53.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.39,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see anything suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:13.75,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't. There's nothing. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:17.24,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Something's weird. Something is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.78,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.03,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.69,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get as far as we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:29.57,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,and once the sun goes down,\N we'll stop and put up our tents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to travel at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:39.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But, man, it's hot. Look, it's 50 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:41.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's always hottest around this time of day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.60,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Eight o'clock? Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:52.06,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro! What time does your clock say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.23,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Ten after eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.97,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Old Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.36,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,So, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.19,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know we lost track of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.97,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,b-but what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.99,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's past 8 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:11.06,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,So why isn't the sun going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:13.74,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:16.60,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The thermometer just jumped \Nto 60 degrees Celsius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.99,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not only is it not going down...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.91,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's actually rising \Nhigher and higher in the west!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.27,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Could that sun be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.07,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,...a Stand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.99,JoJo-Eyecatch3,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(465,1)}The Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:41.99,JoJo-Eyecatch2,sign bot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(958,1)}Arabia Fats
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.54,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:51.54,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Try to hide behind some rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:54.37,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That sun is a Stand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.30,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,We were careless. I didn't realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:02.72,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like we were being watched, \Nbut couldn't see it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:06.78,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, all day long... No, all night long...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.57,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That Stand is planning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.67,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to boil us overnight, like octopuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:11.85,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,and kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:15.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,No. It won't take that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:19.84,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to even be in a \Nsauna for more than thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:22.25,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,How can we fight it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.74,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! It's now 70 degrees Celsius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:30.48,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, we can't even tell \Nif that Stand is close or far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.70,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The distance is impossible to judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:37.21,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,The quickest way to settle \Nthis is to take out the user.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:41.89,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the user... Whoever it is should be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We must find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:46.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been concealing their \Npresence from us somehow while
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.01,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,following us all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.49,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.51,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it's like The Lovers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.98,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that we encountered in Pakistan,\N a Stand that can be remotely controlled?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.06,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's inconceivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:00.88,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A weak Stand can be controlled from a distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:05.35,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure you can feel The Sun's energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.78,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The user must be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.70,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:24.59,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The camels are collapsing from the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.40,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,But just staying still won't help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.97,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use Hierophant to look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.22,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.19,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just find out the enemy Stand's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.66,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,If we know how far away it actually is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.89,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we might be able to find the user.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:42.11,JoJo-main,Green,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty meters. Forty meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:45.28,JoJo-main,green,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty meters. Eighty meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.49,JoJo-main,green,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.05,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.12,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin! Call Hierophant back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.04,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.58,JoJo-main,green,0000,0000,0000,,Before that happens, Emerald...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:00.96,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.04,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.72,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busting a hole in the ground, so get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.70,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Kakyoin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:42.71,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I was in the middle of using Emerald Splash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.35,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That guarded me, so I'm not badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.45,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,B-But more importantly, it's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.09,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm going to go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.87,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That attack was perfectly aimed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:58.42,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the enemy is definitely watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.48,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?! Where's the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.88,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.29,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy will find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:10.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Let's just sit\N tight and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:15.99,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.09,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Things can't go on like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.25,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:44.55,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time for an\N old-timer like me to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.87,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But we're in a bad spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:49.12,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even use my best technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:52.24,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get some information...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:53.67,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.82,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:07.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,How are you watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:10.34,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the enemy invisible or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:12.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kakyoin, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.06,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:19.14,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.24,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right, Kakyoin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:29.71,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jotaro? You, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:40.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You, too, Polnareff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.23,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:53.13,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone's finally lost it because of the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:56.49,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one left who's sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:02.24,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Jotaro, calm down! \NGet a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:08.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The best way to win when the \Ngoing gets rough is to stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.20,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:13.17,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea, Mr. Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.80,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that rock over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.91,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it just big enough for someone to hide behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.17,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:30.10,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Now look at the rock on the opposite side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,On the opposite side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:37.91,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:41.62,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rock that's shaped exactly the same
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.78,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,on the opposite side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.87,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow is also reversed. Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.30,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.95,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way, Old Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro! If you go outside right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.52,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you're all but asking to be attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:00.75,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.60,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,A hole appeared in the air?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:17.11,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. You're pathetic, Old Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:21.71,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just assume that the heat's too much for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:25.87,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it's hard to\N believe you're my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:30.09,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,We've defeated the enemy Stand,\N so it's night now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:32.54,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say it's back to being night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.83,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, we're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:38.05,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan to stay in that hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:44.55,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. It's finally dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:49.86,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:50.98,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.37,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Check out the machines behind this mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.77,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty comfortable.\N It even has air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:02.67,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I didn't realize that \Nhe was reflecting the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.51,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,landscape and tailing us from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:07.78,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,He has a tank of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.16,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll gladly take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.04,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:16.50,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:22.05,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this means... we beat him already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.59,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.35,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know this guy's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:29.68,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but we've already beaten his Stand, The Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:32.57,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,That would be what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:33.10,JoJo-TheSun,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(138,1)}The Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.69,JoJo-TheSun,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun                         {\fs34}Retires
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:38.72,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun card's Stand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:40.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite the opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:43.87,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but once you figure it out, it's pretty stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:47.50,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry to our next destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:50.52,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite chilly in the desert at night, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:53.29,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Traveling at night is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.71,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we might get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:57.36,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,We've defeated our enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:59.69,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can have sweet dreams tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.09,JoJo-main,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Ba-dum-tss.
